#. <section class="sutta" id="an6.47"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an6.47:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 6"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 6"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an6.47:0.2"
msgid "5. Dhammikavagga"
msgstr "5. About Dhammika"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an6.47:0.3"
msgid "47. Paṭhamasandiṭṭhikasutta"
msgstr "47. Realizable in This Very life (1st)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
#. VAR: moḷiyasīvako → moliyasīvako (bj, pts1) | moḷiyasivako (s1-3) | moḷisīvako (mr)
msgctxt "an6.47:1.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho moḷiyasīvako paribbājako yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"bhagavatā saddhiṃ sammodi."
msgstr ""
"And then the wanderer Moliyasīvaka went up to the Buddha, and exchanged "
"greetings with him."

msgctxt "an6.47:1.2"
msgid ""
"Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ "
"nisinno kho moḷiyasīvako paribbājako bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"When the greetings and polite conversation were over, he sat down to one "
"side and said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "an6.47:1.3"
msgid "“‘sandiṭṭhiko dhammo, sandiṭṭhiko dhammo’ti, bhante, vuccati."
msgstr "“Sir, they speak of ‘a teaching realizable in this very life’."

msgctxt "an6.47:1.4"
msgid ""
"Kittāvatā nu kho, bhante, sandiṭṭhiko dhammo hoti akāliko ehipassiko "
"opaneyyiko paccattaṃ veditabbo viññūhī”ti?"
msgstr ""
"In what way is the teaching realizable in this very life, immediately "
"effective, inviting inspection, relevant, so that sensible people can know "
"it for themselves?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.357"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an6.47:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Tena hi, sīvaka, taññevettha paṭipucchāmi. Yathā te khameyya tathā naṃ "
"byākareyyāsi."
msgstr ""
"“Well then, Sīvaka, I’ll ask you about this in return, and you can answer as "
"you like."

msgctxt "an6.47:2.2"
msgid "Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, sīvaka, "
msgstr "What do you think, Sīvaka? "

msgctxt "an6.47:2.3"
msgid ""
"santaṃ vā ajjhattaṃ lobhaṃ ‘atthi me ajjhattaṃ lobho’ti pajānāsi, asantaṃ vā "
"ajjhattaṃ lobhaṃ ‘natthi me ajjhattaṃ lobho’ti pajānāsī”ti?"
msgstr ""
"When there’s greed in you, do you understand ‘I have greed in me’? And when "
"there’s no greed in you, do you understand ‘I have no greed in me’?”"

msgctxt "an6.47:2.4"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bhante”."
msgstr "“Yes, sir.”"

msgctxt "an6.47:2.5"
msgid ""
"“Yaṃ kho tvaṃ, sīvaka, santaṃ vā ajjhattaṃ lobhaṃ ‘atthi me ajjhattaṃ lobho’"
"ti pajānāsi, asantaṃ vā ajjhattaṃ lobhaṃ ‘natthi me ajjhattaṃ lobho’ti "
"pajānāsi—"
msgstr "“Since you know this,"

msgctxt "an6.47:2.6"
msgid "evampi kho, sīvaka, sandiṭṭhiko dhammo hoti … pe …."
msgstr ""
"this is how the teaching is realizable in this very life, immediately "
"effective, inviting inspection, relevant, so that sensible people can know "
"it for themselves."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an6.47:3.1"
msgid "Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, sīvaka, "
msgstr "What do you think, Sīvaka? "

msgctxt "an6.47:3.2"
msgid "santaṃ vā ajjhattaṃ dosaṃ … pe …"
msgstr "When there’s hate …"

msgctxt "an6.47:3.3"
msgid "santaṃ vā ajjhattaṃ mohaṃ … pe …"
msgstr "delusion …"

msgctxt "an6.47:3.4"
msgid "santaṃ vā ajjhattaṃ lobhadhammaṃ … pe …"
msgstr "greedy thoughts …"

msgctxt "an6.47:3.5"
msgid "santaṃ vā ajjhattaṃ dosadhammaṃ … pe …"
msgstr "hateful thoughts …"

msgctxt "an6.47:3.6"
msgid ""
"santaṃ vā ajjhattaṃ mohadhammaṃ ‘atthi me ajjhattaṃ mohadhammo’ti pajānāsi, "
"asantaṃ vā ajjhattaṃ mohadhammaṃ ‘natthi me ajjhattaṃ mohadhammo’ti "
"pajānāsī”ti?"
msgstr ""
"When there are delusional thoughts in you, do you understand ‘I have "
"delusional thoughts in me’? And when there are no delusional thoughts in "
"you, do you understand ‘I have no delusional thoughts in me’?”"

msgctxt "an6.47:3.7"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bhante”."
msgstr "“Yes, sir.”"

msgctxt "an6.47:3.8"
msgid ""
"“Yaṃ kho tvaṃ, sīvaka, santaṃ vā ajjhattaṃ mohadhammaṃ ‘atthi me ajjhattaṃ "
"mohadhammo’ti pajānāsi, asantaṃ vā ajjhattaṃ mohadhammaṃ ‘natthi me "
"ajjhattaṃ mohadhammo’ti pajānāsi—"
msgstr "“Since you know this,"

msgctxt "an6.47:3.9"
msgid ""
"evaṃ kho, sīvaka, sandiṭṭhiko dhammo hoti akāliko ehipassiko opaneyyiko "
"paccattaṃ veditabbo viññūhī”ti."
msgstr ""
"this is how the teaching is realizable in this very life, immediately "
"effective, inviting inspection, relevant, so that sensible people can know "
"it for themselves.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an6.47:4.1"
msgid "“Abhikkantaṃ, bhante, abhikkantaṃ, bhante … pe …"
msgstr "“Excellent, sir! Excellent!"

msgctxt "an6.47:4.2"
msgid ""
"upāsakaṃ maṃ, bhante, bhagavā dhāretu ajjatagge pāṇupetaṃ saraṇaṃ gatan”ti."
msgstr ""
"From this day forth, may the Buddha remember me as a lay follower who has "
"gone for refuge for life.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an6.47:4.3"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ."
msgstr ""
